```mermaid
flowchart TD
    Start([User: Install BMad]) --> Init[/bmad-init]
    
    Init --> CreateFiles[Create project structure<br/>docs/, .claude/, etc.]
    CreateFiles --> SpawnOrch[Spawn BMad Orchestrator<br/>Automated Mode]
    
    SpawnOrch --> Orch{BMad Orchestrator<br/>Running}
    
    Orch -->|Phase Detection| P1[Phase 1: Discovery<br/>Spawn Business Analyst]
    P1 --> P1Done{Product Brief<br/>Created?}
    P1Done -->|Yes| P2[Phase 2: Planning<br/>Spawn PM + UX parallel]
    P1Done -->|No/Stopped| Stop1[Session Stopped<br/>Context full / User interrupt]
    
    P2 --> P2Done{PRD + UX<br/>Created?}
    P2Done -->|Yes| P3[Phase 3: Architecture<br/>Spawn Architect]
    P2Done -->|No/Stopped| Stop2[Session Stopped]
    
    P3 --> P3Done{Architecture<br/>90% Gate?}
    P3Done -->|Yes| P4[Phase 4: Epics<br/>Spawn Scrum Master]
    P3Done -->|No/Stopped| Stop3[Session Stopped]
    
    P4 --> P4Done{Epics +<br/>Sprint Plan?}
    P4Done -->|Yes| P4b[Phase 4b: Stories<br/>Spawn Story Writers<br/>Parallel per Epic]
    P4Done -->|No/Stopped| Stop4[Session Stopped]
    
    P4b --> P4bDone{All Stories<br/>Created?}
    P4bDone -->|Yes| P5Decision{Check Sprint<br/>Scope}
    P4bDone -->|No/Stopped| Stop5[Session Stopped]
    
    P5Decision -->|Small Sprint| P5Team[Phase 5: Implementation<br/>Create Agent Team<br/>DB + Backend + Frontend]
    P5Decision -->|Large Sprint| P5Batch[Phase 5: Batched<br/>Implement 5 stories at a time]
    
    P5Team --> P5Done{All Stories<br/>Done?}
    P5Batch --> P5Done
    P5Done -->|Yes| P6[Phase 6: QA<br/>Spawn QA Engineer]
    P5Done -->|No/Stopped| Stop6[Session Stopped]
    
    P6 --> P6Done{Tests Pass?}
    P6Done -->|Yes| P7[Phase 7: Deploy<br/>Spawn DevOps]
    P6Done -->|No/Stopped| Stop7[Session Stopped]
    
    P7 --> P7Done{Deploy Config<br/>Ready?}
    P7Done -->|Yes| P8[Phase 8: Review<br/>Spawn Tech Lead]
    P7Done -->|No/Stopped| Stop8[Session Stopped]
    
    P8 --> Complete([Project Complete!<br/>Ship Decision])
    
    %% Resume Flow
    Stop1 --> Resume[User: /bmad-next]
    Stop2 --> Resume
    Stop3 --> Resume
    Stop4 --> Resume
    Stop5 --> Resume
    Stop6 --> Resume
    Stop7 --> Resume
    Stop8 --> Resume
    
    Resume --> LoadOrch[Spawn BMad Orchestrator]
    LoadOrch --> ReadTracker[Read session-tracker.md<br/>Detect current phase]
    ReadTracker --> ResumePhase{Resume from<br/>where stopped}
    
    ResumePhase -->|Phase 1| P1
    ResumePhase -->|Phase 2| P2
    ResumePhase -->|Phase 3| P3
    ResumePhase -->|Phase 4| P4
    ResumePhase -->|Phase 4b| P4b
    ResumePhase -->|Phase 5| P5Decision
    ResumePhase -->|Phase 6| P6
    ResumePhase -->|Phase 7| P7
    ResumePhase -->|Phase 8| P8
    
    style Orch fill:#e1f5ff
    style P5Team fill:#ffe1ff
    style Resume fill:#fff4e1
    style Complete fill:#e1ffe1
```
